      "representative_length": 4528,
      "representative_excerpt": "I am writing to strongly oppose the proposed Paper Manifest Sunset Rule, which would eliminate paper manifests in favor of mandatory electronic manifesting (e-Manifest) after a 24-month phase-in period. While I support the goals of improved tracking, data quality, and environmental protection, this rule as proposed is impractical and burdensome for businesse...",
