      "representative_excerpt": "The proposed rule allows electronic signatures on hazardous waste manifests without addressing whether the certifying generator representative must be physically present at the site when the waste shipment is prepared and transferred to the transporter.<br/><br/>The generator certification statement required under 40 CFR 262.23(a) declares that the shipment ...",
