      "representative_length": 3584,
      "representative_excerpt": "Unnecessary Burden on Generator, Transporter, and Disposal Departments<br/>Requiring full transition to electronic manifests would force a complete overhaul of internal processes across entire departments at generators (utilities/industrials), transporters, and disposal facilities. This includes:<br/>New hardware/software procurement and integration.<br/>Ret...",
