      "representative_posted_date": "2026-03-10T04:00:00Z",
      "representative_length": 1984,
      "representative_excerpt": "Summary - Only TSDF's should be required to submit e-manifests and the process should stay the same.<br/>In order for paper manifests to be accepted by the industry the API is going to have to have some way a generator can share a manifest with several Hazardous Waste Transporters and TSDFs BEFORE assigning a transporter or designated facility to the manifes...",
