      "representative_posted_date": "2026-03-09T04:00:00Z",
      "representative_length": 1915,
      "representative_excerpt": "Please forgive my bluntness, I saw this email come thru and although I have better things to do felt the need to add my proverbial 2 cents.<br/>I understand and would agree that hazardous waste should be tracked to ensure proper management and agree that a central system was needed. <br/>The uniform manifest alleviated the need to use a different manifest fo...",
