      "representative_posted_date": "2026-03-11T04:00:00Z",
      "representative_length": 1076,
      "representative_excerpt": "As a state regulator, the most common incorrect form of the manifest we see is the electronic copy. Receiving facilities are not accurate when inputting the information into e-manifest. On top of bad data quality, important information is often not entered at all from box 14 of the manifest into e-manifest. Federal and state waste codes are not entered causi...",
      "submissions": {
