      "page_count": 1,
      "representative_comment_id": "EPA-HQ-OLEM-2025-3456-0006",
      "representative_posted_date": "2026-03-09T04:00:00Z",
      "representative_length": 429,
      "representative_excerpt": "The Department of transportation requires a paper manifest to leave each facility with each shipment. Historically this paper manifest was later scanned into the e-manifest system usually at the disposers on behalf of the original generator. With this proposal it sounds as if you are going to make the generator be the one to create the manifest in the system...",
